        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p3",
            "text": "I loaded my camel with high-quality silk and tea to trade.",
            "cn": "我在骆驼上装载了优质的丝绸和茶叶进行贸易。",
            "emoji": "🐫",
            "notes": "loaded with: 装载...；high-quality: 高品质的；trade: 贸易，交易",
